name: TSE-Request Observability - Jira Escalated
jql: (labels = tse-request AND labels = jira_escalated and labels = tse-high) AND (Engineering Team[Dropdown]" = "KV Observability" OR "Engineering Team[Dropdown]" = "Observability Infrastructure" OR "Engineering Team[Dropdown]" = Observability OR "Engineering Team[Dropdown]" = "Cluster UI") AND NOT (status = Duplicate OR status = Cancelled OR status = Canceled OR status = Done) ORDER BY updated DESC

name: tse-request tse-high jira_escalated
jql: labels = tse-request AND labels = jira_escalated AND labels = tse-high AND (Engineering Team" = "KV Observability" OR "Engineering Team" = "Cluster UI" OR "Engineering Team" = "Observability Infrastructure" OR "Engineering Team" = Observability) AND NOT (status = Duplicate OR status = Cancelled OR status = Done) ORDER BY updated DESC

name: Blocker Highly Regulated
jql: labels = blocker-highly_regulated ORDER BY priority DESC

name: SQL Queries Priority Docs
jql: project = DOC AND issuetype in (Docs) AND status not in (Done, Duplicate, Cancelled) AND priority in (Highest, High) AND Product Area[Dropdown]" = "Data Int - SQL Queries" ORDER BY status DESC

name: SQL Schema & Migrations Priority Docs

column11: High) AND "Product Area[Select List (cascading)]" in ("SQL Schema & Migrations") ORDER BY status DESC

name: SQL Session Priority Docs
jql: project = DOC AND issuetype in (Docs, Epic) AND status in (Backlog, In Progress"
column11: High) AND "Product Area[Dropdown]" = "Data Int - SQL Sessions" ORDER BY status DESC

column11: High) AND "Product Area[Select List (cascading)]" in cascadeOption(10063

name: High Priority Docs
